{{Quote|It's a bitter winter when a smuggler reaches the end of his days. That's where the saying comes from. They call it that because few ever survive it.|[[Fahs Oxsor]]|<ref name="Bitter">{{JournalCite|5|A Bitter Winter}}</ref>}}
'''Bitter Winter''' was the [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]] name for a disease also known as '''Brekken Vinthern''' on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. This affliction struck the elderly and created holes in their memories. [[Toob Ancher]], a [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]], caught this disease during retirement and slowly lost his mind. It had similarities to [[melanncho]].<ref name="Bitter" />

